Mexico border
wall.

00:18.952 --> 00:19.919 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Then:

00:19.953 --> 00:21.454 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

00:21.488 --> 00:23.423 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BERNIE SANDERS (I), Vermont:
Democrats need
a strong, progressive agenda.

00:23.456 --> 00:29.696 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: I sit down
Senator Bernie Sanders
to discuss the Trump agenda and
what Democrats

00:29.729 --> 00:32.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
need to do to start winning
again.

00:32.799 --> 00:36.202 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And dreamers worry about a
potential nightmare.

00:36.236 --> 00:41.374 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Young undocumented immigrants
prepare for
the worst, as the Trump
administration adopts

00:41.408 --> 00:43.209 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a hard-line approach.

00:43.243 --> 00:46.846 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOSE, Undocumented Immigrant:
Losing my job,
losing the ability to teach my
kids, being

00:46.880 --> 00:53.820 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
separated from my family, losing
everything
that I know, I don't think it
can get any

00:53.853 --> 00:55.155 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
worse than that.

00:55.188 --> 01:02.195 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: All that and more
on tonight's
"PBS NewsHour."

01:02.228 --> 01:04.431 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
(BREAK)

