JUDY WOODRUFF: A federal judge
in San Francisco
has blocked President Trump's
order on so-called

01:15.575 --> 01:17.343 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
sanctuary cities.

01:17.377 --> 01:23.249 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
