got a rough
reception today at a women's
summit in Berlin,

07:17.370 --> 07:19.105 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Germany.

07:19.138 --> 07:23.276 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
