discussion, the
audience groaned and hissed as
she argued

07:23.309 --> 07:28.281 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that her father is a -- quote --
"tremendous
champion" of enabling women and
families.

07:28.314 --> 07:33.486 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Later, she dismissed the
reaction as -- quote
-- "politics" and said, "I'm
used to it.

07:33.519 --> 07:35.354 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It's fine."

