25:15.080 --> 25:18.116 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Obama administration had
been negotiating
with the Canadians to come up
with a permanent

25:18.149 --> 25:19.117 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
