47:28.212 --> 47:33.684 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I love that the heroine of the
book is an
anti-heroine, that she's a
human, that she's

47:33.717 --> 47:40.924 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
