have to hold
their enemies closer than their
friends.

47:53.403 --> 47:57.875 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The series is
striking in how
disturbing it is, both in the
dark version

47:57.908 --> 48:03.447 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
