healthier.

48:15.158 --> 48:18.762 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
They're trying to raise
fertility rates.

48:18.795 --> 48:20.063 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Those are all good things.

48:20.097 --> 48:22.199 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's very inviting.

48:22.232 --> 48:28.071 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, we come into our world and
it feels pretty
good, until you look closely.

48:28.105 --> 48:32.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRUCE MILLER, Showrunner, "The
Handmaid's
Tale": Dystopia in our time had
been synonymous

48:32.142 --> 48:38.081 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
